{"tid":509834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜啦，請放低你既故事","createTime":"2017-12-25T17:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T16:34:32.000Z","uid":4637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc8d754443e28526b90703e551739362b8357f7","tid":509834,"uid":4637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T17:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最近好想寫一個關於自己既故事<br />\n最後發現點都落唔到手<br />\n所以想聽下關於大家既故事<br />\n想睇下唔同人既過去<br />\n有乜野執著、煩惱、點睇自己等等<br />\n夜啦，放低你既故事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋放低你既「故事」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc2155ee69904efb7f2f5f76b2bc62864db723d","tid":509834,"uid":110259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T17:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c077237f083d79a13f7817dfbbd237dbcffc71","tid":509834,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T17:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解自己咁無能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解自己咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想專心溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係一溫書就思考人生<br />\n一唔識就好躁好躁<br />\n想同人傾計<br />\n想同人傾訴<br />\n但係講得太多又驚人唔想再理我<br />\n覺得我好煩<br />\n點解我要成日放負<br />\n點解我要喊唔停<br />\n點解日日都想喊<br />\n明明知你都好攰<br />\n明明知你唔想再聽唔想再氹<br />\n但係都好想好想好想放負<br />\n得你先明我<br />\n好攰好攰好攰<br />\n好想死<br />\n但係又唔敢<br />\n好想知道死後會點<br />\n所有野都好想好想<br />\n真係好攰<br />\n點解我專注力咁差<br />\n點解我咁蠢<br />\n點解我一溫書就喊到溫唔到<br />\n點解我會欠你咁多"},{"pid":"a46659a04415af70971dc029de6d7c3f60a61573","tid":509834,"uid":76524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c59bd632b88750349a6aa53c7b299b5d6046a21","tid":509834,"uid":4637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T18:11:26.000Z","msg":"果然呢個世界好多遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d453e14a89f3d6eba13350ae39912556d5bfc99d","tid":509834,"uid":4637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}